title: Apollo 3 - 2010 Album
description:
A Cologne boy band, founded in 2006. The band members are Dario Flick (guitar), Henry Horn (vocals, guitar) and Marvin Schlatter (keyboard, rap vocals).

They came up with their band name after seeing the movie Apolo 13 (1995). They replaced the number 13 with the digit 3 because they are a threesome.
